OL,3,CBoy, 17, jailed for murder of teenager
OL,4,CHarleigh Hepworth in park
OL,6,FA 17-year-old boy has been jailed for
OL,7,Flife for the murder of teenager
OL,8,FHarleigh Hepworth in a park.
OL,10,FThe boy, who can't be named for legal
OL,11,Freasons, was sentenced to a minimum
OL,12,Fterm of 17 years and 42 days, after a
OL,13,Fsix-week trial ending last November.
OL,15,FHarleigh was stabbed in the chest in
OL,16,FWolverhampton's West Park on 7 March
OL,17,Flast year - two weeks after his 17th
OL,18,Fbirthday.
