OL,4,CHarleigh Hepworth in park
OL,6,FThe murderer's accomplice, Jovarn
OL,7,FEsterine, who was 17 at the time but
OL,8,Fnow 18, was sentenced to more than six
OL,9,Fyears for manslaughter.
OL,11,FHarleigh's family described him as
OL,12,F"funny and polite" and said his life
OL,13,Fwas ended through a "moment of
OL,14,Fmindless aggression".
OL,16,FWest Midlands Police said Harleigh was
OL,17,Fvisiting Wolverhampton with a friend
OL,18,Fwhen they were confronted by their two
OL,19,Feventual attackers, who had met them
OL,20,Fwith an "ulterior motive".
