OL,4,CHarleigh Hepworth in park
OL,6,FAfter a brief exchange, Harleigh was
OL,7,Fstabbed in the chest and ran away, but
OL,8,Fwas found lying in the park and later
OL,9,Fdied from his injuries.
OL,11,FAs Harleigh was stabbed, Esterine
OL,12,Fstopped Harleigh's friend from
OL,13,Fintervening, holding a knife to his
OL,14,Fchest and threatening to kill him
OL,15,Funless he told them the passcode to
OL,16,Fhis phone which was then stolen.
OL,18,FEsterine and the 17-year-old ran away
OL,19,Fand discarded one of the stolen phones
OL,20,Fin a nearby drain.
