OL,3,CBoy, 17, jailed for murder of teenager
OL,4,CHarleigh Hepworth in park
OL,6,FIn a statement released after
OL,7,Fconviction, they said: "Our family,
OL,8,Fhis girlfriend and close friends will
OL,9,Fno longer be able to enjoy seeing him
OL,10,Fgrow, mature and enjoy life.
OL,12,F"He had positive plans for his future.
OL,13,FHarleigh had a great sense of humour,
OL,14,Fhe was funny, and he was polite.
OL,16,F"We will miss him massively, but we
OL,17,Fwill always remember his cheekiness,
OL,18,Fhis infectious smile and the fun times
OL,19,Fwe had together.
